name: Tsuyu Asui (Hero) LoRA [72mb]
description:
LoRA for Tsuyu Asui. Pretty versatile with positioning and such, and the dataset is entirely based on her outfit, so good luck getting anything but a green costume :).

Trained on Anything 4.0, but you can use mostly anything. I used my own merge for the detailed refs I posted.

0.7-0.8 Weighting should be fine.

Just tag how you normally would for the character and it should work fine. I'll provide a few to help out.



If you have any LoRA requests and wouldnt mind buying me a Hot Chocolate, please consider going to my page. https://www.buymeacoffee.com/JohnStinko
